Attachments
precis:
Authority for the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign an AMENDMENT to
the SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENT between CANADA and the INTERNATIONAL CIVIL
AVIATION ORGANIZATION concerning the new location of its headquarters in
MONTREAL, Quebec, or (b) to issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing
other officials to sign the Agreement on behalf of Canada.
